  "instructions": [
    "Heat the pistachio oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the ginger, cumin, coriander, and turmeric. Cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the petit pois and roasted red pepper. Cook for 2-3 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper to taste.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer, covered, for 15-20 minutes or until the petit pois are tender.",
    "Garnish with chopped parsley and serve hot.",
    "Serve over couscous or rice, if desired."
